被拘捕，獲准保釋候查，須於七月上旬向警方報到，案件由新界北總區重案組跟進。男警隨後已被警方停職，豈知停職期間再涉嫌犯下強姦案。<br />\n警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍及姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"117264d9a1778793ad9b5e5ad7ad1642bb417895","tid":2273555,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31831ab9d73f3178ed7b2246b8e738467e388391","tid":2273555,"uid":373220,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T23:40:32.000Z","msg":"放心濫暴打示威者就永遠唔會追究"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T00:26:06.000Z","msg":"仲有呀，比假口供嗰啲呢！"},{"pid":"2500fe48ff4f1c33dafeedc9e8fbfc2a066a4640","tid":2273555,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c17cdd22ba37f1d4a029911bb81ee98a4b1eb131","tid":2273555,"uid":229916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T00:11:56.000Z","msg":"大有大貪，細有細貪🥳🥳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T00:26:36.000Z","msg":"未計販冰兵"},{"pid":"18fda656f4899fb4675a9aa35acbd0a517630f89","tid":2273555,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T00:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}